q("php-51", "How do you prevent SQL injection with PDO?", ["Using prepared statements with placeholders", "Escaping strings", "Using addslashes()", "Removing quotes"], 0, "PDO prepared statements with parameterized queries securely separate SQL from data, preventing SQL injection.");
q("php-52", "What does spl_autoload_register() do?", ["Registers a function to automatically load classes when used", "Registers array functions", "Autoloads extensions", "Loads PHP files automatically"], 0, "spl_autoload_register() registers autoload functions that are called when an undefined class is instantiated.");
q("php-53", "What is the difference between abstract class and interface?", ["Abstract classes can have implementations; interfaces only declare signatures", "No difference", "Interfaces can have properties", "Abstract classes cannot have methods"], 0, "Abstract classes can provide method implementations and properties; interfaces (pre-PHP 8) only define method contracts.");
q("php-54", "How does the nullsafe operator (?->) work in PHP 8?", ["Allows safe access to properties/methods when the object might be null", "Creates nullable types", "Assigns null values", "Checks for null"], 0, "The nullsafe operator ?-> short-circuits to null if the left operand is null, preventing errors from calling methods on null.");
